---
name: Onboard Check Point key-value syslog via UDP
description: |
  Reads Check Point syslog over UDP when firewall fields are encoded as
  pipe-delimited key-value pairs in the RFC5424 message field, and publishes
  normalized Check Point records to the topic `checkpoint`.
---

accept_udp "udp://0.0.0.0:514"
this = {...data.parse_syslog(), raw: data}
checkpoint::syslog::parse_kv_message
publish "checkpoint"
